        {
            "book_id": 3,
            "end_cfi": "/2/4/76/1:446",
            "format": "EPUB",
            "highlighted_text": "Bhikkhus, when mindfulness of breathing is developed and cultivated, it is of great fruit and great benefit. When mindfulness of breathing is developed and cultivated, it fulfills the four foundations of mindfulness. When the four foundations of mindfulness are developed and cultivated, they fulfill the seven enlightenment factors. When the seven enlightenment factors are developed and cultivated, they fulfill true knowledge and deliverance.",
            "spine_index": 15,
            "spine_name": "OEBPS/xhtml/Chapter07.html",
